HEADWORD: Cycadaceous
<hw>Cyc`a*da"ceous</hw> <pr>(s?k`?-d?"sh?s ⟦or⟧ s?`k?-)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or resembling, an
